data.title: SecondHandSongs
data.meta_description:
Find out who performed the original version of a particular song, or who covered or sampled that song. Unlike many related
                      sites, we try to be as complete as possible (not just performer and song title, but also songwriters and original releases) and order the data in a reusable and maintainable way.
data.text:
Discover The Original

SecondHandSongs is building the most comprehensive source of cover song information.
